## New Project: waymark
- **Replaces:** gorilla/mux (Go, 98,604 importers, 21.9k stars, 1.9k forks)
- **Why:** Discontinued on endoflife.date. Last commit Aug 2024 (v1.8.0). Was archived Dec 2022, briefly revived July 2023, went inactive again. 23 open issues, 12 unmerged PRs. No drop-in alternative exists — chi/gin/echo require API rewrites, Go 1.22+ stdlib only covers basic routing.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/waymark (verified available)
- **Improvements:** gorilla/mux API compatibility (drop-in migration), active maintenance, Go 1.22+ minimum, better pattern caching, improved error messages, performance optimizations, zero dependencies, compat package for seamless migration
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #711 (scaffolding), #712 (core Router/Route/pattern matching), #713 (middleware/URL building/walking), #714 (compat package + tests), #715 (docs + migration guide)

